- Nope, it's only 5:30.

00:19:04.922 --> 00:19:05.891
- She doesn't have a key,

00:19:05.991 --> 00:19:08.195
so I don't think she'll
be here till 6:00.

00:19:08.295 --> 00:19:08.730
- What?

