Why didn't she hold
onto her key?

00:19:11.168 --> 00:19:13.607
(all laughing)

00:19:13.707 --> 00:19:14.842
- That wig's too weird, Yasu.

00:19:14.942 --> 00:19:15.878
We can't even
talk to you.

00:19:15.978 --> 00:19:19.084
Mika and Masaru put all that
effort into our costumes.

